    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。具体连接方式是：Player通过点击拖拽走子到K1，K2把棋盘状态显示给Player。K1用虚线发InputEvent给K3，K3用虚线发RenderCommand给K2。",
